        {name:"Sorcerer-Warlord",type:"major",aspects:["Phade Knowledge Disguised as Magic", "Rules Through Fear of the Inexplicable", "The People Believe He Cannot Die"],skills:[{name:"Lore",r:5}, {name:"Provoke",r:4}, {name:"Will",r:3}, {name:"Notice",r:3}],stress:3,stunt:"Once per scene, reveal that a situation aspect has been under their control the entire time, gaining a free invoke.",qty:1},
        {name:"Phade Maintenance Drone - Threat Assessment Active",type:"major",aspects:["Operating Within Parameters", "Does Not Distinguish Parties", "Threat Assessment Is Pre-Civilisation"],skills:[{name:"Fight",r:4}, {name:"Notice",r:5}, {name:"Physique",r:4}, {name:"Shoot",r:3}],stress:5,stunt:"Immune to social skills entirely. Once per scene, the drone reclassifies a zone as a restricted area - any character remaining in that zone at the start of the next exchange takes stress automatically.",qty:1},
        {name:"Symbiont-Integrated Warlord Lieutenant",type:"major",aspects:["The Integration Gives and It Takes", "Knows the Vault's Layout Intimately", "Has Been Here Longer Than Any Map"],skills:[{name:"Fight",r:4}, {name:"Notice",r:4}, {name:"Stealth",r:3}, {name:"Lore",r:3}],stress:3,stunt:"Once per scene, the Lieutenant reroutes the symbiont network to create a zone aspect anywhere in the vault with two free invokes - the organisms here respond to their presence.",qty:1},
        {name:"The Alzabo",type:"major",aspects:["It Speaks With the Voices of Those It Has Eaten", "The Memory Is Accurate", "The Body Is Faster Than It Looks"],skills:[{name:"Provoke",r:5}, {name:"Fight",r:3}, {name:"Athletics",r:4}, {name:"Empathy",r:4}],stress:4,stunt:"Once per scene, the Alzabo speaks with the voice of someone a specific PC knew - and delivers one true piece of information that character would have shared. The target must overcome Will at difficulty 3 or spend their action this exchange hesitating.",qty:1},
        {name:"False Prophet of the Phade",type:"major",aspects:["The Claim Is False - The Belief It Commands Is Real", "Controls This Community Through Phade Mystification", "Has a Working Phade Device and Does Not Know What It Does"],skills:[{name:"Rapport",r:5}, {name:"Provoke",r:4}, {name:"Deceive",r:4}, {name:"Will",r:3}],stress:3,stunt:"Once per scene, the Prophet invokes genuine community belief to create a mob aspect - until the party can prove the false claim in public, all social rolls against the community are at -2.",qty:1}
